{
  "articleId": "ahmed_1000_jod_en",
  "locale": "en",
  "title": "Ahmed Earns 1,000 JOD — Why He Still Feels Broke",
  "description": "A real case study: how invisible spending leaks drain a decent salary, and the simple tracking method that changed everything.",
  "tagEn": "CASE STUDY · EXPENSE TRACKING",
  "tagAr": "دراسة حالة · تتبع المصاريف",
  "readMin": 5,
  "publishedDate": "2026-03-31",
  "sections": [
    {
      "id": "sec_ah_1",
      "title": "Ahmed's situation",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "text": "Ahmed is 29. He earns 1,000 JOD per month. And yet, by the end of every month, he feels the same: \"I don't know where my money goes.\""
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "text": "This is not a rare case. It's the norm."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "sec_ah_2",
      "title": "Step 1: The numbers (what Ahmed thinks)",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "text": "Ahmed believes his spending looks like this:"
        },
        {
          "type": "example",
          "title": "Ahmed's estimated budget",
          "rows": [
            { "label": "Rent", "value": "350 JOD" },
            { "label": "Transportation", "value": "150 JOD" },
            { "label": "Food", "value": "200 JOD" },
            { "label": "Other", "value": "300 JOD" },
            { "label": "Total", "value": "1,000 JOD" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "text": "From his perspective, everything is under control."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "sec_ah_3",
      "title": "Step 2: The reality (what actually happens)",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "text": "When Ahmed tracked his spending for one month, the real picture looked different:"
        },
        {
          "type": "example",
          "title": "Ahmed's actual spending",
          "rows": [
            { "label": "Rent", "value": "350 JOD" },
            { "label": "Transportation", "value": "150 JOD" },
            { "label": "Food", "value": "240 JOD" },
            { "label": "Subscriptions", "value": "60 JOD" },
            { "label": "Cafés & dining out", "value": "120 JOD" },
            { "label": "Online purchases", "value": "90 JOD" },
            { "label": "Miscellaneous", "value": "110 JOD" },
            { "label": "Total", "value": "1,120 JOD" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "key_insight",
          "title": "The gap",
          "text": "He was overspending by 120 JOD — without realizing it."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "sec_ah_4",
      "title": "The problem is not income — it's visibility",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "text": "Ahmed's issue is not how much he earns. It's that he doesn't see the full picture."
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "text": "Small expenses:"
        },
        {
          "type": "ul",
          "items": [
            "Feel insignificant individually",
            "But accumulate significantly"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "text": "This is how financial leakage happens."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "sec_ah_5",
      "title": "The hidden pattern",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "text": "Ahmed's spending had three key issues:"
        },
        {
          "type": "ul",
          "items": [
            "Untracked small expenses (coffee, delivery, apps)",
            "Recurring subscriptions he forgot about",
            "No predefined limits per category"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "text": "None of these felt like \"big problems.\" But together, they created a constant deficit."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "sec_ah_6",
      "title": "The turning point",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "text": "After one month of tracking, Ahmed made three simple changes:"
        },
        {
          "type": "ul",
          "items": [
            "Set a limit for dining out",
            "Cancelled unnecessary subscriptions",
            "Reduced impulse purchases"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "text": "Result:"
        },
        {
          "type": "ul",
          "items": [
            "Saved ~150 JOD/month",
            "Reduced stress",
            "Gained control"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "sec_ah_7",
      "title": "What this means for you",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "text": "If you feel like Ahmed, the issue is not discipline. It's clarity. You cannot fix what you cannot see."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "sec_ah_8",
      "title": "What you should do next",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "text": "Track your expenses for 30 days. Use Rasmalak Expense Tracking & Insights to:"
        },
        {
          "type": "ul",
          "items": [
            "Automatically categorize spending",
            "Identify hidden leaks",
            "Get actionable recommendations"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "action_prompt",
          "text": "Then ask Mustasharak: \"Where is my money actually going — and what should I change first?\""
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
